data.description: ** Spectacular 1.94 Acre Ranch Estate Santa Fe style with large 4 BR Main House (Master Bedroom downstairs) & LARGE Guest House with HUGE Master Bedroom & Bathroom & its own kitchen (could be connected to main house), existing furniture included. Beautiful Pool & Spa with waterfall, 8 Car Garage, 5 Stall Barn with runs & tack room, could be a GREAT WORKSHOP with bathroom/laundry & sink, 4 additional large shade stalls and turnouts at front, Large Arena with lights and excellent footing, trail around arena, beautiful mature landscaping surrounding property. Property is 2 separate parcels of .97 Acres each. Close access to 215 Beltway & 95 Fwy in the NW. Property being sold in "As-is" condition, Estate Sale so no fix-ups by seller, needs some TLC, roof leak repair and inside repairs, priced well for a creative Buyer with a vision ** Great opportunity to purchase this incredible one-of-a-kind Estate and at a good price!! ** Perfect for Car and/or Horse enthusiasts **
